Level: 6
Range: 0
Duration: 5 rounds + 1 round/level
Casting Time: 7
Area of Effect: caster
Saving Throw: special

The several attempts of the warlord to control climate have given different results, and it is by improving one of the most exceptional that he came to this result:
when the spell is cast, all the winds in the nearby area wrap around the caster and begin to swirl, turning into a true wind armor. As long as he is protected by this armor, he is protected against gale-force winds, blows all the clouds and flames (+75% fire resistance), deflects all missiles (+10 to AC) and troubles other attacks (+2 to AC). In addition, any creature approaching him must make a saving throw vs. breath or will be violently pushed back 10 meters.
This spell can only be used outdoors.~
